要求：duanyun-fu>=40，guiyuan-tunafa>=50，neili>=100
命中与威力相关：duanyun-fu

tiaoyan 挑眼式
要求：guiyuan-tunafa>=50，neili>=300
命中与威力相关：exp，duanyun-fu

